(jenkins)integrate->Plan->code->build->test->integrate
integrate->deploy->monitor->integrate(Jenkins)

Jenkins is a Continuous Integration tool that allows continuous development, test and deployment of newly created codes.
(Jenkins là một công cụ tích hợp liên tục cho phép phát triển, kiểm tra và triển khai liên tục các mã mới được tạo.)

Step:
- Prerequisites and installation
- Jenkins typical configurations
- Create new users and manage permissions
- build freestyle jobs and schedule its run
- integrate github with jenkins
- SMTP configguration for sending emails
- deploy maven based web-app to Tomcat server
- Distributed build: master - Slave configuration and set-up
- Backing up jenkins
